The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of skepticism in every professional field. The report focuses primarily on auditing and scientific skepticism, which may not fully represent skepticism's application in other areas. Additionally, the lack of recent publications may limit the applicability of some strategies in rapidly evolving fields. Further research and expert consultations could provide more comprehensive insights into enhancing skepticism across various domains.

